headline: Centene Texas Push Links 2025 Community Plans With Valuation Debate
summary: Superior HealthPlan, a Centene (NYSE:CNC) subsidiary, outlined its 2025 community impact plan in Texas. The plan includes partnerships with more than 800 organizations across the state. Superior expects to participate in over 2,100 local events and fund new health programs and facilities. For investors tracking NYSE:CNC, this update adds a community-focused layer to a stock that has faced mixed recent performance.
